proof_script:
lemma nfoldli_mono[refine_mono]: "\<lbrakk> \<And>x s. f x s \<le> f' x s \<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> nfoldli l c f \<sigma> \<le> nfoldli l c f' \<sigma>" "\<lbrakk> \<And>x s. flat_ge (f x s) (f' x s) \<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> flat_ge (nfoldli l c f \<sigma>) (nfoldli l c f' \<sigma>)"
apply (induct l arbitrary: \<sigma>, simp+)
apply (simp_all add: bind_mono)
done
